                    "id": 4,
                    "type": "fill-blank",
                    "question": "She ___ three languages. (speak)",
                    "correct": [
                        "speaks"
                    ],
                    "explanation": "Use 'speaks' with 'she' (third person singular). Add 's' to the base verb."
                },
                {
                    "id": 5,
